ect-mapped BTB helps CoreMark's repeated taken loops by avoiding warm branch redirects, but IF-side predictor lookup/update logic and aliasing keep the gain modest.","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"cores/bench/LESSONS.md","time":{"start":1778636694120,"end":1778636694126}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0c9e7999a59fe287016a03d795fe58819aa12e787c510b617b"}},"id":"prt_e1f02224b001RiIhCmzMa2iUeZ","sessionID":"ses_1e0fdfa0affea77BgisF9SD2SE","messageID":"msg_e1f020631001H0E49Kwi0JySPs"}}
