ual next PC, raise redirect only on prediction mismatch, and expose branch predictor update information for taken/not-taken outcomes and targets.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/core.sv\", \"description\": \"Wire predictor update signals between EX and IF while preserving the existing NRE... (line truncated to 2000 chars)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/log.jsonl","time":{"start":1778636700032,"end":1778636700037}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_070211e4004e790c016a03d79be9148199bd5c0e0b5c333d57"}},"id":"prt_e1f02396e001V9lvU0Sj4pdOf5","sessionID":"ses_1e0fdfa0affea77BgisF9SD2SE","messageID":"msg_e1f0223f3001zXqdbfiiU5gt54"}}
