{"type":"text","timestamp":1778670747475,"sessionID":"ses_1def73698ffeM2YkNch3jE8WZx","part":{"id":"prt_e2109b84e001jm2u8viw14pyo5","messageID":"msg_e21091ae5002UsXaa0l2a30geY","sessionID":"ses_1def73698ffeM2YkNch3jE8WZx","type":"text","text":"The history favors behavior-preserving local reductions in EX/MEM datapath width and rejects broader predictor/control rewrites. I’m going to propose a narrowly scoped EX-stage common-subexpression micro-opt that does not touch the nret contract or prior failed AUIPC/control-bit changes.","time":{"start":1778670745678,"end":1778670747473},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0aa46bfb4434a4e0016a045c9990fc819a831fd7eecaf2a074","phase":"commentary"}}}}
