{"type":"text","timestamp":1778646558139,"sessionID":"ses_1e0680950ffeZxzoQM9CK3XRti","part":{"id":"prt_e1f98a2ee001sP19uwAU3BHRln","messageID":"msg_e1f981661001WrGSADQpXb0568","sessionID":"ses_1e0680950ffeZxzoQM9CK3XRti","type":"text","text":"Prior `micro_opt` wins were local critical-path reductions, while broader control/divider changes regressed. I’m going to propose a similarly local ALU multiply datapath consolidation: one signedness-selected 33x33 product instead of three parallel 64-bit products.","time":{"start":1778646557422,"end":1778646558138},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_022bd2cc8166d4a4016a03fe1d24448198a834a6b41027d3e8","phase":"commentary"}}}}
