{"type":"text","timestamp":1778654456513,"sessionID":"ses_1dfef2e2bffeNR1xJ9ZgdbqeaU","part":{"id":"prt_e20112994001YieDqcbrJjhcdj","messageID":"msg_e2010edd4001e99MyINURgy4cr","sessionID":"ses_1dfef2e2bffeNR1xJ9ZgdbqeaU","type":"text","text":"The prior `micro_opt` wins are narrowly local reductions in critical-path or state width; the regressions came from adding control complexity. I’m going to keep this proposal local: reduce unused EX/MEM payload flops and routing rather than changing predictor or pipeline behavior.","time":{"start":1778654456212,"end":1778654456512},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_021da585dbb4250f016a041cf8195c81999a67545af37a77a6","phase":"commentary"}}}}
