{"type":"text","timestamp":1778656599343,"sessionID":"ses_1dfce6a9effe77WsWqR6kQ5gs1","part":{"id":"prt_e2031d28d001c8vs3A57FjPBhR","messageID":"msg_e2031c037001HynZELy4jrPaUC","sessionID":"ses_1dfce6a9effe77WsWqR6kQ5gs1","type":"text","text":"The history points to local timing and payload reductions as the reliable micro-opt pattern; predictor policy/capacity and load-bubble removal have recently regressed. I’m going to propose another behavior-preserving payload/control simplification rather than a new front-end feature.","time":{"start":1778656596621,"end":1778656599340},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_07958dd9afd844f8016a04255484ac819b8ede95df664b0890","phase":"commentary"}}}}
