ol bundle construction.\"\n+  - file: rtl/mem_stage.sv\n+    description: \"Use ctrl.mem_read instead of ctrl.mem_to_reg for MEM-stage forwarding of formatted load data.\"\n+  - file: rtl/wb_stage.sv\n+    description: \"Use ctrl.mem_read as the writeback mux select between read_data and alu_result.\"\n","additions":34,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-001-r8s0.yaml","time":{"start":1778656619928,"end":1778656619933}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_082b4db902feb4ff016a0425620c64819abaed20eb0dab5e88"}},"id":"prt_e2032076c001l04qxubVNOLwpW","sessionID":"ses_1dfce6a9effe77WsWqR6kQ5gs1","messageID":"msg_e2031dde0001BF5cY4xgTnfrhs"}}
