{"type":"text","timestamp":1778662159944,"sessionID":"ses_1df7a4916ffe8B8q0dMz2Ncyu1","part":{"id":"prt_e2086b1c2001wcQScLR48uCoIm","messageID":"msg_e20862957001ihXDu2J4D8QW2S","sessionID":"ses_1df7a4916ffe8B8q0dMz2Ncyu1","type":"text","text":"The structural history is mostly negative for bigger pipeline changes, but the positive results cluster around reducing hot payload/fanout while preserving the MEM/WB boundary. I’m writing a narrower structural hypothesis that keeps MEM/WB retirement but splits the hot writeback/forward state from RVFI-only shadow state.","time":{"start":1778662158786,"end":1778662159942},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0ba4b7049670091d016a043b0ea24481989172345413d277ee","phase":"commentary"}}}}
