{"type":"text","timestamp":1778664567352,"sessionID":"ses_1df56634cffeA8ilqgDJLgvhwn","part":{"id":"prt_e20ab6541001r5brFFJqzwwxYv","messageID":"msg_e20aa027f001OU6kKAC3CL6E3o","sessionID":"ses_1df56634cffeA8ilqgDJLgvhwn","type":"text","text":"The structural history is mostly negative for added buffering, early control, store posting, and MEM/WB reshaping. I’m choosing a narrower structural retiming: isolate load/store address generation from the full RV32IM ALU result path, because it follows the prior successful pattern of local datapath isolation without changing IPC semantics.","time":{"start":1778664564033,"end":1778664567351},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_042b8b71164b4613016a044473ebec819ba03bf945e3aed0cf","phase":"commentary"}}}}
