{"type":"text","timestamp":1778670767603,"sessionID":"ses_1def73626ffeYKtoPSemtBHeh1","part":{"id":"prt_e2109fd18001RiH4jUDDvcV1Rj","messageID":"msg_e210904a9001THyb8Jg9tgNoxh","sessionID":"ses_1def73626ffeYKtoPSemtBHeh1","type":"text","text":"The structural history favors small datapath isolation over added buffers, early control, or predictor state. I’m writing a focused hypothesis that extends the successful LSU/JAL result-producer split with a fast ADD/SUB/AUIPC lane, avoiding the failed M-lane and control-flow restructuring patterns.","time":{"start":1778670763288,"end":1778670767602},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_009006bbc1acd7c9016a045caaaa7481988d05d3f39ee537d3","phase":"commentary"}}}}
