{"type":"text","timestamp":1778646632566,"sessionID":"ses_1e06809b2ffeHGTgP6G1vzU1HB","part":{"id":"prt_e1f99c870001mtJXInT4GvDxMB","messageID":"msg_e1f983866002gZxZM11jhEZytj","sessionID":"ses_1e06809b2ffeHGTgP6G1vzU1HB","type":"text","text":"I’m going to write a store-buffer structural hypothesis: hide random dmem stalls for ordinary RAM stores with a one-entry posted store buffer, while preserving ordering by draining before later memory ops and not posting MMIO marker/UART stores.","time":{"start":1778646632560,"end":1778646632564},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0798c24743da1e7e016a03fe684cec819993fe2fb625f58904","phase":"commentary"}}}}
