old and flush controls between hazard, IF, and ID without changing the NRET=1 top-level RVFI or memory port contract.\"\n","additions":32,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r6s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778652341997,"end":1778652342001}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_038f8d3739972d05016a0414ab930c81988b0bffaab06c8780"}},"id":"prt_e1ff0be8c001b7dK7Ml7Ethtbi","sessionID":"ses_1e00ff80dffes22j7NX1ZsgBh6","messageID":"msg_e1ff0a80e002jK7ib4bxYjUk0d"}}
