ad-use forwarding made the MEM load-result path feed same-cycle EX operands and redirect control, so CoreMark bubble savings did not offset the longer dmem-to-EX critical path.","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"cores/bench/LESSONS.md","time":{"start":1778670704195,"end":1778670704223}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_04185fe3fbe7eabf016a045c700f40819a8e359c95b15b1e9c"}},"id":"prt_e21091623001ATef6X64xHGrSJ","sessionID":"ses_1def735c0ffe7cKiOb0Czje8hi","messageID":"msg_e2108ca770015BWAWWgqqpJRRP"}}
