{"type":"text","timestamp":1778670727417,"sessionID":"ses_1def735c0ffe7cKiOb0Czje8hi","part":{"id":"prt_e21096828001vq5ckSN8S0Npki","messageID":"msg_e210916a8001JLniY443yca7AL","sessionID":"ses_1def735c0ffe7cKiOb0Czje8hi","type":"text","text":"The predictor history rules out bigger tables, RAS/victim state, IF instruction predecode, update filtering, delayed updates, and prediction-validation metadata. I’m choosing a narrowly scoped predictor-state split that preserves the proven 16-entry PC-only BTB lookup while removing conditional-counter training from unconditional jumps.","time":{"start":1778670725160,"end":1778670727416},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0f49a47092e89d33016a045c85104c819a83c2cafe3f405165","phase":"commentary"}}}}
