{"type":"text","timestamp":1778649104305,"sessionID":"ses_1e040db50ffexyXDpRosXL3pJb","part":{"id":"prt_e1fbf7a41001qsBBkXciigmphu","messageID":"msg_e1fbf4a1e002bM882Tl199taZr","sessionID":"ses_1e040db50ffexyXDpRosXL3pJb","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor history shows the plain 16-entry PC-indexed BTB helped, while instruction-data IF predecode, RAS, and added update-policy compares regressed or broke. The safest next predictor hypothesis is therefore an aliasing-capacity change that keeps the IF lookup PC-only and does not add fetched-instruction decode to the next-PC path.","time":{"start":1778649102913,"end":1778649104303},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_02f0689f68ed6ea7016a04080ed374819bab3b217c71091e63","phase":"commentary"}}}}
